PN,30601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,FWatch in full as Artemis II splashes
OL,6,Fdown after historic trip around the
OL,7,Fmoon.
OL,9,FArtemis II's astronauts completed the
OL,10,Ffirst lunar voyage in more than half a
OL,11,Fcentury, landing safely in the Pacific
OL,12,FOcean on Friday.
OL,14,FWith their flight now complete, the
OL,15,Ffour astronauts have set NASA up for a
OL,16,Fmoon landing by another crew in just
OL,17,Ftwo years and a future permanent moon
OL,18,Fbase within the decade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
