OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,FObserving the far side of the moon,
OL,6,Fthe astronauts asked permission to
OL,7,Fname a pair of craters after their
OL,8,Fmoonship and Wiseman's late wife,
OL,9,FCarroll.
OL,11,F"We are back in the business of
OL,12,Fsending astronauts to the moon,
OL,13,Fbringing them back safely and to set
OL,14,Fup for a series more," Isaacman said.
OL,15,F"This is just the beginning."
OL,26,@sD@AOUvD@VO]wD@AOUwD@]O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/12
