PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,FTheir moonshot drew global attention
OL,6,Fas well as star power, earning praise
OL,7,Ffrom President Donald Trump, Canadian
OL,8,FPrime Minister Mark Carney, Britain's
OL,9,FKing Charles III, Ryan Gosling, star
OL,10,Fof the latest space flick Project Hail
OL,11,FMary, and even Captain Kirk himself,
OL,12,FWilliam Shatner of TV's original Star
OL,13,FTrek.
OL,15,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
