OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,FDespite its rich scientific yield, the
OL,6,Fnearly ten-day flight was not without
OL,7,Ftechnical issues. Both the capsule's
OL,8,Fdrinking water and propellant systems
OL,9,Fwere hit with valve problems. In
OL,10,Fperhaps the most high-profile
OL,11,Fpredicament, the toilet kept
OL,12,Fmalfunctioning, but the astronauts
OL,13,Fshrugged it all off.
OL,15,FAs for the heat shield, military
OL,16,Faircraft crews photographed it from
OL,17,Fafar during reentry, and divers
OL,18,Fchecked it from underneath as the
OL,19,Fcapsule floated in the Pacific. More
OL,20,Fdetailed examinations are planned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,F"We can't explore deeper unless we are
OL,6,Fdoing a few things that are
OL,7,Finconvenient," Koch said, "unless
OL,8,Fwe're making a few sacrifices, unless
OL,9,Fwe're taking a few risks, and those
OL,10,Fthings are all worth it."
OL,12,FHansen added: "You do a lot of testing
OL,13,Fon the ground, but your final test is
OL,14,Fwhen you get this hardware to space
OL,15,Fand it's a doozy."
OL,26,@mD@AOUoD@NO]oD@[OUrD@YO]tD@OOUwD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/12
