OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,FUnder the revamped Artemis program,
OL,6,Fnext year's Artemis III will see
OL,7,Fastronauts practice docking their
OL,8,Fcapsule with a lunar lander or two in
OL,9,Forbit around Earth. Artemis IV will
OL,10,Fattempt to land a crew of two near the
OL,11,Fmoon's south pole in 2028.
OL,13,FThe Artemis II astronauts' allegiance
OL,14,Fwas to those future crews, Wiseman
OL,15,Fsaid.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/12
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1775909467
OL,3,CArtemis II crew return safely to Earth
OL,5,F"But we really hoped in our soul is
OL,6,Fthat we could, for just for a moment,
OL,7,Fhave the world pause and remember that
OL,8,Fthis is a beautiful planet and a very
OL,9,Fspecial place in our universe, and we
OL,10,Fshould all cherish what we have been
OL,11,Fgifted," he said.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
